data.description: Welcome to this stunning home for sale located in the heart of Temple, TX! This beautifully crafted home boasts 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 full baths, offering plenty of room for a family. As you enter the home, you will be welcomed by the warm and inviting living room, complete with hard surface flooring and ample natural light. The spacious layout is perfect for family movie nights or entertaining guests. The modern kitchen features ample countertop space, modern appliances, and plenty of cabinet storage, making meal prep a breeze! Step outside to the perfectly shaded backyard, perfect for hosting family gatherings and cookouts. The large patio provides the perfect place to enjoy a morning cup of coffee or unwind after a long day at work. Located minutes away from shopping, dining, and entertainment options, don't miss out on the opportunity to make this stunning home your own!
